🔐 Smart Secured Surveillance System (PFA Project)
📌 System Architecture (IMPORTANT)

This project follows a client–server architecture:

🖥️ Client Application
server_search.exe
Lightweight interface used to access the system
Sends requests to the server for video search / retrieval
🌐 Server Side (Core System)
All AI processing, encryption, and video handling happens here
Handles:
Video recording
YOLOv8 object detection
AES-256 encryption/decryption
Video storage
HTTP streaming server

👉 The client does NOT process AI or encryption locally — it only interacts with the server.
--------------------------------------------------------------
📌 Overview

The Smart Secured Surveillance System is an AI-powered secure video surveillance platform that integrates:

Real-time object detection using YOLOv8
Strong encryption using AES-256-CBC
Secure client–server communication for video access and retrieval

The system ensures confidential, tamper-resistant, and remotely accessible surveillance data, even in untrusted environments.
-----------------------------------------------------------------
🚀 Key Features
🎥 Real-Time Video Recording
OpenCV-based video capture
Continuous surveillance support
🧠 AI Object Detection
YOLOv8 integration
Real-time intelligent detection and monitoring
🔐 Encryption Layer
AES-256-CBC encryption for video files
Password-based key derivation
Chunk-based encryption for large files
PKCS7 padding for security integrity
🌐 Client–Server System
Lightweight client: server_search.exe
Server handles:
Video processing
Storage
Streaming
Secure file access
📊 Security Analysis Module
NPCR (pixel change rate)
UACI (intensity variation)
Entropy analysis
Correlation analysis
Encryption/decryption performance benchmarking
Histogram comparison
-----------------------------------------------
🛠️ Tech Stack
Python 3.8+
OpenCV
Ultralytics YOLOv8
Cryptography (AES-256-CBC)
NumPy / SciPy
HTTP Server / Requests
PyInstaller (for .exe client)
------------------------------------------------------
📦 Installation
git clone https://github.com/Rayen-mizouri/Smart-Secured-Surveillance-System.git
cd Smart-Secured-Surveillance-System
pip install -r requirements.txt
--------------------------------------------------------
▶️ Usage

Start Server (Core System)
python video_server.py
python yolo.py
----------------------------------
Run Client Application
server_search.exe
